name: DANGER DAGGER KNIFE NECKLACE
description:
SNASH JEWELRY presents this rugged little functioning knife. The perfect go-to for any tiny-knife emergency. Equipped with an antique gold plated chain, this UNISEX piece hangs at the perfect length to accompany every summer wardrobe. 

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: NYC SKYLINE CUT-OUT NECKLACE
description:
Show your love for this awesome town! This NYC skyline necklace rests approximately 2" long and comes on a 16" chain with a bonus 2" connector. 

This necklace is cast in solid brass and polished to a high shine. Also available plated in antique gold, antique silver, and partially blackened sterling silver.

name: DOUBLE FINGER NYC SKYLINE CUT-OUT RING
description:
This ring is amazing. Period. Celebrate an awesome city with this kick-ass double finger ring. 

This piece comes in either a highly polished yellow or white brass. It fits over two fingers - and has an adjustable band (adjustable with pliers). Let us know the sizes of the two fingers you'd like to wear it and we'll custom size it. If you need further size adjustment, any plier will help you do the trick!

name: PEANUT GALLERY DOUBLE RING
description: A brand new design from SNASH JEWELRY, the Peanut Gallery Double Ring features a row of people hanging out on a bench—and hanging with you throughout the day! Cast in bronze, then partially blackened to bring out the details, this double finger ring is a little gritty, just the way we like it.

name: ASYMMETRIC ELECTRIC STUD EARRINGS
description:
This adorable set of asymmetric lightning bolts are an awesome riff on your classic everyday accessory. These babies are available in blackened brass (as pictured), high polished gold plating over bronze, or an antiqued matt silver over bronze. 

All earrings as equipped with sterling silver ear posts and ear backs.

name: TRICERETOPS HALFSIES
description:
New from SNASH JEWELRY is this adorable triceretops - cut in two! With one side heads and one side tails, this charming little piece is perfect for all dino-lovers. Equipped with sterling silver earposts and earnuts, these bronze dinos are richy plated in either a a matt-finished antique gold or antique silver.  

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: CADAVER DOUBLE TOOTH RING
description: Cast in solid bronze or white bronze, these are exact replicas of cadaver teeth - fully adjustable, this piece fits over two fingers.

name: FANCY FLAMINGO STUD EARRINGS
description:
It's always summer, somewhere...

...only available in rose gold - these thickly plated flamingos are cast in bronze and equipped with sterling silver earposts and earnuts. 

Be the envy of all your beach buddies and sport these birdies year round.

name: PEANUT GALLERY NECKLACE
description:
Cast in brass with a matching brass chain, this partially blackened necklace features a fabulous row of friends hanging out - the perfect treat for the oddball on your wishlist!

Hangs from a 24" chain!

Choose from partially blacked brass (as pictured) or partially blacked white bronze!

name: SHEATH NECKLACE
description:
New to SNASH JEWELRY is this heavy-duty knife sheath - this UNISEX necklace is cast as a single piece - hangs from a longer 24" chain - perfect for laying for the ladies and gents in your life.

Cast in bronze and hand-blackened, this piece is paired with a matching chain.

Available in white or yellow bronze

name: DANGER DAGGER NECKLACE - GUNMETAL
description:
The perfect go-to for all of your tiny-knife emergencies, this functional pocketknife hangs from a braided gunmetal chain. Designed for knife-wielding men and women, the Danger Dagger Necklace by SNASH JEWELRY truly cuts through any style competition.

Hangs from a 24" chain

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: SIDESHOW DEER RING
description:
Come on down to the SNASH SIDESHOW and feast your eyes on our new studio pet. This siamese deer ring will keep you protected during all your daily little adventures… a little intimidating, a little sweet - perfect for all.

CAST IN BRONZE, plated thickly in antique gold or antique silver. Also available in sterling silver with either a polished or oxidized finish, or raw blackened bronze. 

Please specify color choice and size!

SIZE CHOICES - 5,6,7,8,9,10

name: GHOSTFACE EARRINGS
description:
Video game characters never looked this good. (Aside from Ms. Pac Man, maybe.) 

The ghoulish, but totally great GhostFace Earrings from SNASH JEWELRY are cast in bronze and richly plated in antique silver or antique gold. They make us super nostalgic (and just a little scared).

H .125" W .25" D .25”. Sterling silver posts and backs.

name: VOYEUR EARRINGS
description:
The sweet little statues in the Voyeur Earrings are a hilarious break from staid studs of the past. This gorgeously detailed duo—one man with binoculars, and a woman sipping from her chalice—are available in antique gold or antique silver for a conversation-starting look that will turn everyone into…well, voyeurs.

H .125" W .25" D .25”. Sterling silver posts and backs.

name: ONE BORED MAN EARRINGS
description:
The sweet little statues in the One Bored Man Earrings are a hilarious break from staid studs of the past. Crafted in bronze and then plated in antique silver or gold, this gorgeously detailed duo—one man, and one woman— are a guaranteed conversations starter.

H .125" W .25" D .25”. Sterling silver posts and backs.

name: READERS RING
description:
This delicate Readers Ring features a couple lost in the Sunday crossword. Cast in bronze or white bronze, this piece is partially blackened to bring out the delightful duo’s meticulous details.

H .125" W .25" D .25”.

Size 5-9 available

name: VOYEUR RING
description:
The sweet little statues in the Voyeur Ring are a hilarious break from staid bands we’re used to. SNASH JEWELRY crafted this gorgeously detailed duo—one man with binoculars, and a woman sipping from her chalice—in brass (pictured) or white bronze, then partially blackened it for a conversation-starting look that will turn everyone into…well, voyeurs.

H .125" W .25" D .25”.

Size 5-9 - special sizing upon request

name: ONE BORED MAN NECKLACE
description:
The adorable scene displayed on the One Bored Man Necklace is a hilarious break from staid pendants of the past. 

Available in partially blackened yellow brass (pictured) and partially blackened white bronze, this gorgeously detailed piece is a guaranteed  conversation starter. 

Hangs from a 20" chain. Pendant: H .75" W 1" D .25”.

name: MIGRATION DOUBLE RING
description:
Take your ensemble into flight with the MIGRATION DOUBLE FINGER RING by SNASH JEWELRY. Cast in solid white or yellow bronze, this piece slides comfortable over two fingers and is the perfect accessory for your year-round adventures. 

Blackened and hand brushed by the designer, this piece features two ring shanks that can be adjusted for that perfect fit, but please specify your closest size at checkout!

name: LUCKY PENNY EARRINGS
description:
These delicate little pennies are prefect for everyday wear. Cast in sterling silver, we plated the fronts of each piece in a rich antique gold. You get one side of each penny with each pair. Want them in silver? No problem! Selecting "partially oxidized fronts" in the drop down box gets you an unplated pair - hand blackened and finished to bring out maximum penny details.

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

*PLEASE NOTE THESE PENNIES ARE PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: LONDON SKYLINE DOUBLE
description: Show some love for our neighbor across the pond - London's iconic skyline cast and polished in white or below brass.

name: LANDING EAGLE STUDS
description:
These eagles earrings by SNASH JEWELRY are a must for any bird fan. Perched and ready to land, these highly detailed eagles are cast in bronze and plated in a highly polished antique gold or antique silver to bring out details. 

Equipped with sterling silver ear nuts and ear backs.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: DIAMOND PEGASUS STUDS
description:
This magical pair of Diamond Pegasus Earrings by SNASH JEWELRY feature two diamonds set in each pair, each on the tip of where the Pegasus wings meet. Let these majestic creatures guide you safely through your day and stir up some magic to keep things interesting.

Hans-oxidized sterling silver. Sterling silver ear posts. Two diamonds total in each pair - one on each side.

name: DENTAL RECORD NECKLACE
description:
Who doesn't want to wear a mouth around their neck, right? The Dental Record Necklace by SNASH JEWELRY features a bronze-casted, antique gold-plated dental piece to finally satisfy your tooth-jewelry craving.

Cast in bronze and richly plate in antique gold.

name: CLAW WEAVE RING
description:
A take on our SINGLE CLAW RING, this style features two bird hands intertwined. Buy this style for your sweetheart. This ring, as it is not fully round, contours the finger perfectly.

This ring is cast in bronze and thickly plated in antique gold or antique silver. It is also available in partially blackened sterling silver, or polished sterling silver.

name: THE PIZZASAURUS NECKLACE
description:
Pizzasaurus LOVES pizza. So does everyone on the planet. Celebrate your love and share your pizza passion with the world…

This heavy duty pendant hangs from a 24" chain, perfect for both the guys and the gals…

Also available in partially oxidized sterling silver with a matching sterling silver chain.

name: YARD BONE NECKLACE
description: It’s a little warm to wear your mink in the summer, but with the Yard Bone Necklace by SNASH JEWELRY you can at least wear, err, part on a mink. This necklace features two gold-plated pendants cast in the shape of a mink penis, and it hangs from a contrasting gunmetal chain.

name: WOLFIE HALFSIES
description:
Part of SNASH JEWELRY’s latest summer collection, these sterling silver Wolfie Earrings let your earlobes have their own little wolf pack. One side heads, one side tails, this charming, hand-oxidized piece is perfect for all werewolf fans.

Hand-oxidized sterling silver earrings with sterling silver earposts and earnuts

name: LONG BIRD STUDS
description:
These long bird earrings by SNASH JEWELRY are a perfect addition to any accessory collection. Delicately hanging from the tip of the wing, these birds are 1 - 1/4" long. Equipped with sterling silver ear posts and ear nuts, the birds are cast in bronze and then plated in a highly polished antique gold to enhance details. 

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: TREX HALFSIES
description:
Trex Halfsies = a Trex cut in two! New from SNASH JEWELRY is this fierce pair of dino studs - half in one ear, half in the other. Equipped with sterling silver earposts and earnuts, these bronze dinos are richy plated in a matt-finished antique silver or antique gold. 

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: PROTECTASAURUS
description:
This dinosaur is holding onto his favorite possession… protecting his pet chicken from harm all day long. Perfect for somebody you want to hang onto always - to protect from danger wherever it may lurk.

This heavy duty pendant hangs from a 24" chain, perfect for both the guys and the gals…

Also available in partially oxidized sterling silver with a matching sterling silver chain.

name: SUMMER GOLD / GUNMETAL BRACELET DUO
description:
GOLD/GUNMETAL SET

SNASH JEWELRY presents a simple set of two ID-style cuffs - wear on their own or layer with others to add a little subtle toughness to any outfit. You get one gunmetal and one gold. 

ONE SIZE FITS MOST WRISTS from 6" to 7 3/4"

name: NYC SKYLINE BRACELET
description:
SNASH JEWELRY's brand new hinged ID-style bracelet was designed in New York - by a New Yorker - for all fans of this fantastic city. The simple cut-out silhouette of this iconic skyline is perfect for everyday wear. 

Cast in brass, this bracelet is available in three colors - gold, silver or gunmetal. 

ONE SIZE FITS MOST - WRISTS 6" - 7 3/4"

name: CIRCLE CROSSES
description:
Only these earrings can keep you from sinning…

These unisex circle earrings are made from solid brass and richly plated in antique gold or silver. Equipped with sterling silver ear posts and ear nuts. 

ONE SIZE

name: PIGS TEETH STUDS - SHORT
description:
These highly detailed pigs teeth were cast in bronze, richly plated in silver or gold and equipped with sterling silver ear posts and ear nuts. 

UNISEX

name: OUTLINE BRACELET
description:
Pick up one of these stackable cuffs by SNASH JEWELRY and let them jingle and jangle with the best from your own collection. Available in gold, gunmetal or silver, pick up a few and mix and match with your other styles!

ONE SIZE FITS MOST WRISTS from 6" - 7-3/4"

name: ROADRUNNER EARRINGS
description:
These roadrunner earrings are cast in bronze and richly plated in antique gold or antique silver. Equipped with sterling silver ear posts and earnuts. 

UNISEX.

name: PIGS TEETH STUDS - LONG
description:
A longer style of our PIGS TEETH STUDS - these are slightly more angled and a bit more rugged for that clubbing' look. 

Equipped with sterling silver earposts and earnuts - these highly detailed pieces are cast in bronze and plated in antique silver or antique gold. 

UNISEX

name: ZAPPY BRACELET
description:
SNASH JEWELRY presents this ID-style stackable bracelet. This swing-top ID piece is made from solid brass and plated in gunmetal, gold, or silver. Mix and match with our other bracelets!

UNISEX - ONE SIZE FITS MOST - 6" - 7-3/4"

name: AF CUFF
description:
SNASH JEWELRY presents this single silver plated ID stlye cuff - a subtle rugged design to wear on its own or layer with others to acceseroize any look. Get a few colors and stack with our other styles! 

Made from solid brass and plated in antique gold or gunmetal

UNISEX - ONE SIZE FITS MOST WRISTS from 6" to 7-3/4"

name: SQUARE CUT-OUT CUFF
description:
SNASH JEWELRY presents this square cut-out bracelet - great for stacking with our other cuff designs. Made from solid brass, this plated cuff fists most wrists from 6" to 7-3/4. Can be slightly bended once on the wrist for that perfect fit. Do not over-extend. 

ONE SIZE FITS MOST.

name: LEROY BRACELET
description:
SNASH JEWELRY presents this single silver plated ID stlye cuff - a subtle rugged design to wear on its own or layer with others to acceseroize any look. Get a few colors and stack with our other styles! 

Made from solid brass and plated in an antique silver or antique gold to enhance all details. 

UNISEX - ONE SIZE FITS most wrists from 6" - 7-3/4"

name: CUTOUT CROSS
description:
These cut-out crosses are sure to keep you from sinning…. maybe. 

Brass crosses plated in antique gold or antique silver. 

Sterling silver ear posts and ear nuts.

name: EYELASH CASCADE
description:
This half-version of out 12-TOE CASCADE DESIGN features a smaller cascade of asymmetrical bird claws that form a subtle eyelash shape. 

Equipped with sterling silver ear posts, these are UNISEX. 

Cast in bronze, these pieces are richly plated in an antique gold or antique silver.

name: DANGER DAGGER KNIFE NECKLACE - COPPER
description:
SNASH JEWELRY presents this rugged little functioning knife. The perfect go-to for any tiny-knife emergency. Equipped with a copper ball chain and brass snap clasp, this UNISEX piece hangs at the perfect length to accompany every summer wardrobe. 

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

COPPER/GOLD

name: NYC SKYLINE CUTOUT NECKLACE
description:
Everyone loves New York! SNASH JEWELRY brings you this iconic silhouette necklace - perfect for New Yorkers near and far. The cut-out design is perfect for layering with other pieces or over your favorite summer tank. 

Richly plated in silver or gold, the pendant hangs from an adjustable 16-18" double link chain.

name: NYC TIE CLIP
description:
SNASH JEWELRY's brand new skyline tie-clip was designed in New York - by a New Yorker - for all fans of this fantastic city. 

The simple cut-out silhouette of this iconic skyline is perfect for everyday wear. Don't wear ties? This piece also makes an excellent sweater clip.

name: RACE CAR STUDS
description:
These race cars are an awesome and unusual addition to any earring collection. Cast in bronze and plated in a rich antique gold or antique silver, these highly detailed cars are equipped with sterling silver earposts and ear nuts. 

UNISEX - ONE SIZE FITS ALL.

name: MINK PENIS STUDS
description:
Mink penis bones? Yes. 

These ferocious bones curve to create an elegant shape to adorn every lobe. Cast in bronze, these stud-style earrings are available in antique gold, antique silver or gunmetal. 

Equipped with sterling silver ear posts and ear nuts. 

Unisex design - one size fits all

name: STEGOSAURUS HALFSIES
description:
Stegosaurus Halfsies = a stegosaurus cut in two! New from SNASH JEWELRY is this fierce pair of dino studs - half in one ear, half in the other. Equipped with sterling silver earposts and earnuts, these bronze dinos are richy plated in a matt-finished antique silver or antique gold. 

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: OPEN FACED BRACELET SET
description:
SNASH JEWELRY presents this set of two open-faced ID stlye cuffs. A perfect addition to any bracelet collection!

The tops of each of these bracelets work on a hinge and open by gently squeezing each piece at its base. Great for layering!

In this set you will receive one gold and one silver piece. 

ONE SIZE FITS MOSTS WRISTS from 6" to 7 3/4"

SILVER/GOLD SET

name: TREX FLATS
description:
Brand new from SNASH JEWELRY are these fierce and flat TREX studs. Equipped with sterling silver earposts and earnuts, these bronze dinos are richy plated in a polished antique gold or antique silver to bring out every dino detail. 

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: RAM HEAD EARRINGS
description:
These ram heads are perfect for any AIRES, or any fan of this majestic animal.

Available in partially oxidized sterling silver or sterling silver with an antique gold plating.

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

*PLEASE NOTE THESE RAM HEADS ARE PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: BURGERSAURUS NECKLACE
description:
Meet BURGERSAURUS. This dinosaur, like most of us, loves burgers with all the fixins'. Celebrate your love for burgers with this fabulous necklace.

On a 24" chain, this heavy duty pendant is UNISEX.

Cast in bronze, choose from an antique gold or sterling plating.

name: MAJESTIC VERTEBRAE EARRINGS
description:
These pieces are cast directly from the vertebrae of a majestic and mystical creature. No majestic creatures were harmed in making these earrings.

The fronts of these earrings are cast in bronze and plated in antique gold or antique silver. All ear posts and ear nuts are solid sterling silver.

Also available in a highly polished sterling silver with no oxidation.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: TRIPLE ASYMMETRICAL STACK RING
description:
This ring is the most heavy duty one we have - a deluxe version of our SINGLE and DOUBLE ASYMMETRICAL STACK RINGS,  this one will for sure ward off enemies.

Using tiny bird toes to form a cascade of spikes, there are three staggered layers here that form this highly detailed piece.

This ring is UNISEX.

Cast in bronze and plated in an antique gold, antique sliver, polished or partially blackened sterling silver. Available in sizes 5-10

*PLEASE NOTE THIS RING IS PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: MOOSE HEAD EARRINGS
description:
Great for lounging in the log cabin, or strolling around the city...

Available in partially oxidized sterling silver or sterling silver with an antique gold plating.

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

*PLEASE NOTE THESE MOOSE HEADS ARE PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: FULL HANDS EARRINGS
description:
These full hand bird earrings are one of our shop favorites. These look amazing on everyone - a full bird claw, slightly curved - totally ferocious.

The fronts of these earrings are cast in bronze and plated in antique gold or antique silver. We also have these available in a partially oxidized sterling silver.

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs - we leave these unplated.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: HEART CLAW NECKLACE
description:
This fierce little necklace is going to blow you away... Or claw your heart to pieces...

Featuring two legs donated by a late pheasant friend, these little toes form an awesome heart that hangs right under your collar bone. Get one for your girlfriend. Or ex-girlfriend. She'll love you forever. Or spite you. And probably want to marry you.

The pendant hangs about 3" at the widest and will really stand on its' own as the most amazing necklace you own.

Cast in bronze and plated in gunmetal, antique gold plating , or partially blackened sterling silver.  Comes with a 14/16" chain  (this is the prefect length to fit right under the collarbone)  or a 18/20" chain.

name: DINO JAW RING
description:
This piece is cast from the lower jaw of a very tiny, yet ferocious dinosaur. It definitely makes a statement. Make even more of a statement by completing the dinosaur bite - order two or more and get 20% each additional.

CAST IN BRONZE, plated thickly in antique gold or antique silver. Also available in sterling silver with either a polished or oxidized finish.

SIZE CHOICES - 5,6,7,8,9,10

name: DUAL SKUNK JAW NECKLACE
description:
Show the skunks in your life who they're messing with!

Cast from the jaw of an actual skunk, this unisex pendant is sure to keep the vermin away.... Skunk fan? Fret not - these jaws were naturally gathered. Made from two separate jaws, folded, molded... and brought back to life for your enjoyment. 

Jaw measures 1 1/8" wide by 1 1/4" long and is fabulously plated in either antique gold, antique silver or gunmetal. Also available to solid sterling silver. 

Chain measures 22/24"

name: SINGLE ASYMMETRICAL STACK RING
description:
A single version of OUR DOUBLE AND TRIPLE ASYMMETRICAL STACK RINGS, this piece is great for stacking or wearing on its own. 

A cascade of bird toes form this single layer of spikes. This ring is available in two styles - OPEN OR CLOSED (see images).

Cast in bronze and plated in either an antique silver or gold. Also available in a partially blackened sterling silver. Sizes 5-10

*PLEASE NOTE THIS RING IS PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: LUCKY HORSESHOE EARRINGS
description:
These sterling silver horseshoes will bring you everything you're wishing for. Before putting them on, hold them in your hand and make a wish. Throughout the day … good things will happen.

These horse shoes come in a partially blackened sterling silver.

All of our earrings are equipped with sterling silver ear posts and nuts.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: BACONASAURUS NECKLACE
description:
Meet the BACONASAURUS. Over at SNASH JEWELRY, we really love bacon - even vegan bacon! Tell the world that you aren't a vegetarian... or wear it as a vegetarian and be ironic... either way... impress the world and get strangers to talk to you! It really works!

This heavy duty dinosaur skull is devouring a defenseless pig. Amazing. Period. 

Cast in bronze, this piece is available in an antique gold plating, antique silver plating, or gunmetal. 

This piece come on a 24" chain and is UNISEX.

name: DOUBLE ASYMMETRICAL STACK RING
description:
This ring is hardcore - here, we used a cascade of tiny bird claws to create this highly detailed spiky creation.

UNISEX.

Cast in bronze and plated in an antique gold, antique sliver, polished or partially blackened sterling silver. Available in sizes 5-10.

*PLEASE NOTE THIS RING IS PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: DEAD DEER NECKLACE
description:
Things didn't go so well for this little guy … but despite everything, he is thrilled to live on as a fantastic piece of jewelry…

This pieces hangs from a 24" chain. Available in antique gold or antique silver over bronze.

UNISEX.

name: FLAMIN' HEART NECKLACE
description:
This heart is on fire. A cascade of bird toes formed around heart base make up this spiky number - buy this for the love of your life.

Choose from a 16/18" chain or a longer 20/22" version.

Cast in bronze and plated in an antique gold, antique sliver, polished or partially blackened sterling silver.

name: GANG CLAW NECKLACE
description:
A take on our SINGLE BIRD CLAW, this bird is flashing its very non-violent bird-gang sign.

Hangs on an 24" chain.

Cast in bronze and available in antique gold, antique silver, gunmetal plating, or sterling silver. This piece in UNISEX.

name: DIAMOND RING NECKLACE
description:
Hanging from a long 24" chain is this adorable diamond ring. Set in the cast diamond are two CZ stones. 

This piece is UNISEX.

name: SCISSOR SNIP EARRINGS
description:
These adorable little scissors are cast in sterling silver. Also available in an antique plating over sterling. 

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs .

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

*PLEASE NOTE THESE SCISSORS ARE PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: BIRD CLAW NECKLACE
description:
This bird claw necklace hangs at 24" - right over your heart. A perfect piece for layering, or wear solo and be fabulous.

Cast in bronze and available in antique gold, antique silver, gunmetal plating, or sterling silver. This piece in UNISEX.

name: CHILLAXSAURUS NECKLACE
description:
Meet the CHILLAXSAURUS! Only recently have the fossils of this dinosaur been found - used to hot climates, it must wear glasses to protect its sensitive vision. Because of its small T-REX-like hands, the CHILLAXSAURUS is forced to carry his pet human baby in its mouth.

On a 24" chain, this heavy duty pendant is UNISEX.

Cast in bronze, choose from an antique gold or sterling plating.

name: GRILLZ NECKLACE
description:
This grill necklace has been made by casting an actual tooth partial. This is of of our favorites - definitely make a statement with this one!

This piece is UNISEX. It comes on a 24" chain with a 2" connector. The chain is a thick double link that looks GREAT layered with other pieces.

Cast in bronze, choose from an antique sterling, antique gold, or gunmetal plating.

name: MOLAR RING
description:
Cast from two actual molars, this ring is totally neat-o.

Available in partially oxidized sterling silver or sterling silver with an antique gold plating.

SIZES 5-10 available

name: SAFETY PIN EARRINGS
description:
Fabulous, simple, sterling earrings. Available in partially oxidized sterling silver, or with an antique gold plating over sterling silver.

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

*PLEASE NOTE THESE SAFETY PINS ARE PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: RIBCAGE RING
description:
Is that a ribcage on your finger? Turn some heads with this one for sure!

Available in antique gold, antique silver or sterling silver with partial oxidation. Sizes 5-10

name: BULLET CUFFLINKS
description:
Cast from real bullets, these cufflinks are badass. Buy them for somebody special, they deserve it.  
                   
Available in antique silver or antique gold plating over bronze or in a polished solid sterling silver.

ONE SIZE

name: SIDESHOW DEER NECKLACE
description:
Like our favorite SIDESHOW DEER RING, this necklace will keep you protected during all your daily little adventures… a little intimidating, a little sweet - perfect for all.

CHAIN LENGTH OPTIONS 16"/18", 20"/22", 24"/26"Cast in bronze, plated thickly in antique gold or antique silver. Also available in sterling silver.

Please specify color choice and chain length - each length comes with a hidden 2" connector. The 16"/18" and 20/22" options come with the smaller chain pictured - the  24/26" option comes with the thicker chain pictured. Both styles are UNISEX.

name: SHRUNKEN SKULL EARRINGS
description:
These shrunken skulls are simple yet fierce additions to any collection.

Available in antique gold or silver over bronze or sterling silver.

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs .

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: CREATURE RING
description:
This piece is cast from the tooth of an enormous mystical creature. With a hammered band that gently wraps up the finger, this ferocious ring sits comfortably from knuckle to knuckle.

Please select color and size at checkout! Plated options are cast in bronze, sterling options come partially hand-oxdized to bring out details. 

Sizes 5-10 available.

name: ASYMMETRICAL BIRDIE TOE EARRINGS
description:
These earrings are a light-weight version of our FULL HAND earrings. In this pair, you get two birdie toes - one long and one short. No pair is exactly alike. Pictured in an antique gold plating, these asymmetrical pieces are also available in partially blacked sterling silver, polished sterling silver, or gunmetal. 

All asymmetrical birdie toes are cast in sterling silver. The plating, if chosen, only covers the fronts of these pieces. Choose your favorite color at checkout!

*PLEASE NOTE THESE EARRINGS ARE PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: DOLLA DOLLA EARRINGS
description:
Everyone loves money. Show off your love with these fabulous sterling silver dollar bills - partially blackened to enhance every dolla dolla detail. If you'd like gold bills, please specify at checkout.

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

* please note these dollas are photographed on a mirror!

name: 90's FLIP PHONE EARRINGS
description:
Call me, baby. 

These little cell phones are sterling silver and are partially blackened to enhance every digit… Also available in an antique gold plating, please specify at checkout.

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: RIBCAGE & MARBLE NECKLACE
description:
Encased between two anatomical ribs rests a little marble - safely nestled  in a house of bone.

Cast in bronze and plated in antique gold, this ribcage necklace is like none other.

Marble color may vary as it is handpicked just for you by the designer herself. Feel free to message us your top color choices.

This piece hangs from a  24" chain. This piece is UNISEX.

name: PEPPERONI EARRINGS
description:
Borrowed from our favorite PIZZASAURUS necklace, these mini pepperoni earrings are simple reminders of your favorite pizza slice.

Cast in sterling silver, we plated the fronts of each piece in a rich antique gold. Want them in silver? No problem! Selecting "partially oxidized fronts" in the drop down box gets you an unplated pair - hand blackened and finished to bring out maximum pepperoni details.

All earrings come equipped with sterling silver ear posts and backs.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

*PLEASE NOTE THESE PEPPERONIS ARE PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR

name: DINO POINT EARRINGS
description:
These sweet little dinosaurs just want to hang out with you all day! So let them!

The fronts of these earrings are cast in bronze and plated in antique gold or antique silver. All ear posts and ear nuts are solid sterling silver.

Also available in a highly polished sterling silver with no oxidation.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

*PLEASE NOTE THESE DINO POINTS ARE PHOTOGRAPHED ON A MIRROR!

name: PIGGIE HALFSIES
description:
Only YOU can make this piggie whole again…

The fronts of these earrings are cast in bronze and plated in antique gold or antique silver. All ear posts and ear nuts are solid sterling silver.
Also available in a highly polished sterling silver with no oxidation.

ONE SIZE FITS ALL

name: TWELVE TOE EARRINGS
description:
These rugged hand-modelled spikey earrings by SNASH JEWELRY are perfectly pieced together using a variety of staggered bird talons. 

Available in an antique gold, antique sterling, gunmetal plating or solid sterling silver. 

All of our earrings have sterling posts and backs that are left unplated.

name: SINGLE CLAW TWIST RING
description:
Clutching your finger gently are these little birdie claws - cuddling your finger throughout the day. 

Like our DOUBLE BIRD WRAP RING, this piece is as comfortable as it comes. This ring is not fully round - it contours the finger nicely for that perfect fit. 

This ring is cast in bronze and thickly plated in antique gold or antique silver. It is also available in partially blackened sterling silver, or plated sterling.

name: PIG IN PAN NECKLACE
description:
Who doesn't love bacon? No, really...

This necklace is for bacon fans everywhere! 

You get two pendants - a pig in a frying pan and the spatula needed to flip it. Both have been plated in an oxidized silver finish.

Pendants hang from a 22/24" chain and is available with an antique gold or antique sterling plating.

UNISEX.

name: DOUBLE CLAW RING
description:
This is quite possibly the most fierce double finger ring in the whole world. Definitely the most comfortable you will ever wear... 

Cast from a once-adorable pheasant, these legs join together to clutch your fingers all day long... Left open in the front, this ring does not restrain your normal finger motion like other rings do... and it can even be adjusted SLIGHTLY for that perfect fit. 

Please order the closest appropriate size from the selection below and message me the requested size. This piece is cast in bronze and thickly plated in sterling silver. Chirp.

Small - Fits 5 - 6.5 (so dainty!)
Medium - 7 - 9 (most people select this size)
Large - 9.5 - 12 (appropriate for men or otherwise larger hands)

This ring is available in a variety of ways, so pay attention.
FIRST - PICK YOUR SIZE! Small fits sizes 5-6.5 Medium fits 7-9 Large fits 9.5-11.5 MEDIUM is the most common size to order
SECOND - PICK YOUR COLOR! This ring is available in antique gold plating, antique silver plating, gunmetal and sterling silver. Each color is available in MATT or POLISHED. These choices are pictured!

UNISEX.
